cast.overview: A celebrity model couple are invited on a luxury cruise for the uber-rich, helmed by an unhinged, alcoholic captain. What first appears Instagrammable ends catastrophically, leaving the survivors stranded on a desert island in a struggle of hierarchy.
cast.title: Triangle of Sadness

details.biography: Linnea Olsson, born in 1983, is a Swedish singer-songwriter and multi-instrumentalist who is best known as a cellist. She was one of the leading figures in the band Isildurs Bane before releasing her first solo album Ah! in 2012. And she gained major international recognition as a backing singer during Peter Gabriel's Back to Front Tour in 2012.
details.name: Linnea Olsson
